headline.print_headline: Austrian Conservatives Win EU Vote, Far Right Gains-TV
headline.main: Austrian Conservatives Win EU Vote, Far Right Gains-TV

lead_paragraph: Austria's far-right Freedom Party (FPO) advanced to a fifth of the vote in an European Union election on Sunday that the centre-right People's Party was again set to win, initial projections by ORF television showed.
